<div class="container mx-auto mt-8 px-4 py-8 bg-gray-800 rounded-lg shadow-lg max-w-2xl text-gray-100">
  <h1 class="text-3xl font-semibold mb-6 text-gray-100">About This App</h1>

  <p class="mb-4">
    This is a simple chat application built with Rails 8 and Turbo, inspired by the Gemini UI.
    It utilizes the RubyLLM gem for interacting with language models.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-4">
    The goal of this project is to demonstrate a modern Rails application using Turbo Streams for real-time updates
    and integrating with large language models.
  </p>

  <p class="mb-4">
    Feel free to explore the code on <a href="https://github.com/palladius/rails8-turbo-chat" class="text-blue-400 hover:underline">GitHub</a>.
  </p>

  <p>
    Thanks to Emiliano and Christian for their great contributions to the repo..
  </p>

  <div class="flex justify-center my-8">
    <%= image_tag "rails8-gemini-cute.png", alt: "Rails 8 Gemini Chat", class: "rounded-lg shadow-lg" %>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-6 text-center">
    <%= link_to "Back to Chats", chats_path, class: "text-blue-400 hover:underline" %>
  </div>
</div>
